 K & M Accountants Luton 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 About Us 
 Unlike traditional high street Accountants,  K & M Accountants is a  modern firm  of Professional Accountants in Luton. Due to our proactive Accounting, Bookkeeping, Payroll, CIS and VAT services we have achieve significant growth in recent years. 
 We believe that accountancy is  not just about numbers  it's about  adding value  to   your business by being p roactive and forward looking . Therefore we make sure that our clients are informed on a timely basis. 
 At K & M Accountants Luton, Bedfordshire,  we operate on a  flexible  basis as we understand that some clients are unable to take a  time off during office hours  in order to meet us hence we offer a  free weekend or evening meeting facilities  at either client's premises or at our premises.  
 All of our clients are given free and unlimited phone and email support so you can always get 100% free Bookkeeping & VAT advice about  MAKING TAX DIGITAL  in Luton.  
 Our approach is  simple and fair . We agree fee in advance and all of our  fees are fixed  for at least two years so you could always be assured a quality service. 
 Thanks to our proactive text and emails reminder system, our clients are always up to date with their key filling dead lines.  
 Our clients always acknowledge our best service and therefore we are proud to share that K & M Accountants Luton is one of the Five Star rated Accountancy Firm in Luton, Bedfordshire 
